03:23.083 --> 03:24.016
Sophia.

03:24.084 --> 03:25.384
What are we doing here?

03:54.152 --> 03:55.085
How did you know?

03:55.153 --> 03:56.520
Gerard.

03:56.588 --> 03:59.690
He said the portal would
impact the Earth's procession,

03:59.758 --> 04:03.060
that we'd feel the effects
along the 38th parallel

04:03.128 --> 04:04.462
as the time grew near.

04:04.530 --> 04:06.764
The portal is creating a door
in the fabric of space

04:06.832 --> 04:09.067
and we just cracked it open.

04:09.134 --> 04:12.805
Sophia...I know you have
mixed feelings

04:12.873 --> 04:15.508
about what we're doing
to the native population.

04:15.575 --> 04:17.877
But think about the alternative.

04:17.945 --> 04:20.313
Our people are arriving soon.

04:20.380 --> 04:24.017
I don't have the luxury
of self-doubt.

04:24.084 --> 04:26.319
We have to get this done.

